snippet.title: DELTARUNE Chapter 1 - Announce Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The award-winning indie RPG, UNDERTALE, expands the series with a brand new game...in a different world – DELTARUNE Chapter 1! Create your own avatar, meet strange friends, and jump into the darkness starting Feb. 28. http://www.deltarune.com/

#NintendoSwitch #Deltarune
